		<hr size="1">Hate to sound like a total prick, but it's</P><P>USE</P><P>not</P><P>YOUSE.</P><P><BR>Seeing as how that word was used twice (topic and original post), I thought a tiny English lesson was in order.</P><P>Thank you <img src='http://www.everlore.com/gimages/smile.gif' width=15 height=15 align=middle></P><P>As for pets, I tend to favor the water pet.<BR>In a group with 2 mages, though, and the pets aren't tanking, it's *really* fun to have 2 air pets up.  When fighting casters, it's awesome.</P><P>Air pet's special attack is a caster interrupt. *Great* asset.<BR><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
