		<hr size="1">This is my experience, its just mine, I know in advance that others will have other experiences. </P><P>With that out of the way, growing up in GFay I learned a little about what pets to use there. Fire and Earth and Water are good for soloing. Fire because of their ds, and high powered nuke. Water decent hps and a nuke. Earth root very useful if it dies, gives you about ten seconds to run like hell, and the best hp. Air is only useful if you are in a group that is fighting caster mobs. Its stun spell will help keep you and your group alive. Fire is good in groups, mainly if u have a tank. Earth and water are very useful in groups if u dont have a primary tank. And if u ds them before a big fight they are about as good as fire.</P><P>Thats my 2cp (dang now I'm broke)</P><P>Yilnyen <BR>17 mage<BR>Quellious (spelling?)<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
